    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p><em>Greeting: \"The frigid veil persists.\" | Response: \"All the world in winter's white.\" | Parting: \"May her blessing chill you.\"</em></p><p>Only three Nix Mater exist at once \u2014 Fury, Anger, and Wrath. They are the keepers of the Creed of Auril in Icewind Dale, slowly transforming themselves into powerful hag-like crones with Auril's blessing. They compete with each other to become Auril's exarch. Darkvision 60 ft. AC 17 (natural armor). 11th-level caster, DC 16, +8. Ice Walk trait.</p><p><strong>CR 9 \u2014 Deadly</strong></p><p><em>\"Only we can preserve the unspoiled beauty of the world.\"</em></p>"
